=== Components ===
* [[/wiki2html.awk|wiki2html.awk]]: text prozessor
* [[/wiki.cgi|wiki.cgi]]: symlink to wiki2html.awk

==== Optional ====
* [[/wiki.css|wiki.css]]: Stylesheet
* header: <span style='color:red'>TODO</span>
* footer: <span style='color:red'>TODO</span>

=== Limits ===
The page name must be between 3 and 32 characters long. They can contain letters (A-Z, a-z), numbers (0-9) or underscores (_).

=== Syntax ===
compatible to the MediaWiki-Textformat <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Formatting</ref> and/or partially to MoinMoin <ref>http://moinmo.in/</ref>

=== Character formatting ====
Creole formating
|=
| {{{ **bold** }}}                           | **bold**
| {{{ //italic// }}}                         | //italic//
| {{{  **//bold and italic//** }}}           | **//bold and italic//**
| {{{  //**italic and bold**// }}}           | //**italic and bold**//
| {{{  **bold** or //italic// }}}            | **bold** or //italic//
| {{{  //italic// or **bold**  }}}           | //italic// or **bold**
| {{{  //** not italic and not bold //** }}} | //** not italic and not bold //**
| {{{  **// not bold and not italic **// }}} | **// not bold and not italic **//
MediaWiki formating
{|
 | <nowiki> ''italic'' </nowiki>                         || ''italic'' 
 |-
 | <nowiki> '''bold''' </nowiki>                         || '''bold'''
 |-
 | <nowiki> '''''bold & italic''''' </nowiki>            || '''''bold & italic''''' 
 |}
==== Lists ====
{|
 |
 # numbered item 1
 # numbered item 2
 ## numbered sub item 2.1
 ## numbered sub item 2.2
 # numbered item 3
 |
# numbered item 1
# numbered item 2
## numbered sub item 2.1
## numbered sub item 2.2
# numbered item 3
 |-
 |
 * unnumbered item 1
 * unnumbered item 2
 ** unnumbered sub item 2.1
 ** unnumbered sub item 2.2
 * unnumbered item 3
 |
* unnumbered item 1
* unnumbered item 2
** unnumbered sub item 2.1
** unnumbered sub item 2.2
* unnumbered item 3
 |}
=== Definition list ===
{|
 |
 ; title
 : definition 1
 : definition 2
 :: definition 2.1
 |
; title
: definition 1
: definition 2
:: definition 2.1
 |}

==== Mixed list ====
see [[#Bullet list]] & [[#Numbered list]]

=== Preformatted text ==
==== single line code ====
 code#

==== multi line code ====
 code# pwd
 /
==== HTML tag: <pre> ====
{<pre>
pre-
formatet
text</pre>}

==== Links ====
*local link [[#Syntax]]
*internal link to [[other]] wiki page <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links#Internal_links</ref>
*piped link with different text [[papierformat|a3]] <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links#Interwiki_links</ref>
*external link to other websites http://www.heise.de <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links#External_links</ref>
*external link with different text [http://www.heise.de heise online] <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links#External_links</ref>
*external link numbered [http://www.kernel.org] <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Links#External_links</ref>
*HTML link <a href="http://www.heise.de">go to heise.de</a>

==== Tables ====
* Creole table <ref>http://www.wikicreole.org/wiki/Creole1.0#section-Creole1.0-Tables</ref>
|=Heading Col 1 |=Heading Col 2         |
|Cell 1.1       |Two lines\\in Cell 1.2 |
|Cell 2.1       |Cell 2.2               |

* MediaWiki tables <ref>http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Help:Tables</ref>
{|
! head1  !! head2     !! head3
|-
| Orange || Apple     || 12,333.00
|-
| Bread  || Pie       || 500.00
|-
| Butter || Ice cream || 1.00
|}

* another example
{| border="1"
|Orange
|Apple
|align="right" | 12,333.00
|-
|Bread
|Pie
|align="right" | 500.00
|- style="font-style:italic; color:green;"
|Butter
|Ice cream
|align="right" | 1.00
|}

===== cell alignment detection =====
|= Heading Col 1 |= Heading Col 2 |= Heading Col 3 |
|           right|  center        |left            | 
| 1,234.56       |  -             | 1.2.3          |
|      not right | not center     | left ?         |

